text: Neolepetopsis occulta is a species of sea snail, a true limpet, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Neolepetopsidae, one of the families of true limpets. ==Description== ==Distribution== Green Seamount == Habitat == hydrothermal vents ==References== ==External links== * Category:Neolepetopsidae Category:Gastropods described in 1990
title: Neolepetopsis occulta
